ActJobs, Growth and Long-term Prosperity Act
SubjectOrder Fixing November 25, 2013 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing November 25, 2013 as the day on which section 132, subsections 133(1), (3) and (4), sections 135 to 138, subsection 139(2), sections 140 and 141, subsections 142(2) to (4) 144(2) to (6), 145(2) to (4) and 147(1) to (5), (7), (9) and (10), section 148, subsections 149(2) and (5) and sections 152 and 153, of the JOBS, GROWTH AND LONG-TERM PROSPERITY ACT, chapter 19 of the Statutes of Canada, 2012, COME INTO FORCE.
